<refsection role="introduction">
<title>Introduction</title>
<para>The <tag>p:validate-with-nvdl</tag> step applies <biblioref linkend="iso19757-4"/> validation to the
        <port>source</port> document.</para>
</refsection>

<refsection role="step-declaration">
<title>Step declaration</title>
<xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../xmlcalabash/src/main/resources/com/xmlcalabash/library.xpl" xpointer="xpath(/*/*[@type='p:validate-with-nvdl'])"/>
</refsection>

<refsection role="errors"><title>Errors</title><para>
<error code="C0154">It is a <glossterm>dynamic error</glossterm> 
        if the document supplied on <port>nvdl</port> port is not a valid NVDL document.</error>
<error code="C0053">It is a <glossterm>dynamic error</glossterm> if the <option>assert-valid</option> option on
      <tag>p:validate-with-nvdl</tag> is
          <literal>true</literal> and the input document is not valid.</error>
</para>
</refsection>

